{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":4,"day":11}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"讽刺诗二首","authors":["石河"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“双突”进行曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快填快报快快快！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快提快调快快快！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“首长”令下如山倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急如星火莫迟怠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一茬一茬提干部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罹虏恕薄糁U/右上〗①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娉龅吃薄薄糁U/右上〗②"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“双突”火线好气派！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能吹能骗是“天才”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能砸能抢是“将才”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能拍能溜是“奇才”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能钻能爬是“干才”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“武斗将军”当厂长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“阿飞司令”上讲台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戏痞待命任“部长”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单等“特大喜讯”来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②在“四人帮”支持下，有人居然持枪要挟党委，强迫纳新、提干，曰：“枪杆子里面出党员。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧荒谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垦荒史上奇闻一桩："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看咱“帮”中央“放火烧荒”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“荒”在哪里？军区、军委、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“军阀”头上；如何“烧”法？“造反”，炮轰，大嗡大嚷……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄赳赳地亲临现场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙不迭地调兵遣将；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边，江妖婆拍着胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边，王洪文挥起大棒："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“揭不开就砸，砸不开就炸！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煞是热闹，“慷慨激昂”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“烧荒”烧进军营里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知咱心里这样想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睁睁“新天朝”要开张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杆子怎能不姓“帮”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碍事的“烧”光，帅印儿到手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"底下的戏文儿由咱们唱……"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}